  "_corrections": "Applied after the 2026-06-26 adversarial verification pass (verify-hyperlinks workflow). block_forms = never link (generic English / false positives). prefer_module_forms = bare component names that, in fit/loadout prose, should target the module not the blueprint group. ship_default_role = override the default role dossier for a bare ship mention.",
